# New CoverKit use case

Follow [`.cursor/skills/new-usecase/SKILL.md`](../skills/new-usecase/SKILL.md) for the full workflow.

**Summary:** Scaffold one plugin under `plugins/coverkit-usecase-<kebab>/` with a **complete WordPress plugin header**, `coverkit_init` registration (priority 5), and optional `CoverKit\Use_Case` subclass. Reference: `plugins/coverkit-usecase-starter/`.

**Wire up:** README use cases table, `composer run docs:skills`, `composer run lint:php`.
